snippet.title: Hell Pie - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming to Steam in 2021

Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/889910/Hell_Pie/

Hell Pie is a filthy 3d Platformer. Jump, run, swing and fight your way through a variety of open and linear levels. Collect tons of stuff and use Nugget, the chubby angel, to swing around and smash your enemies. Meet deranged characters and find disgusting pie ingredients in a weird, twisted world.
